OL,3,CLabour vows to crack down on tax
OL,4,Cdodgers to fund NHS and schools pledges
OL,6,FITV News Political Reporter Harry
OL,7,FHorton explains how Labour will fund
OL,8,Fits spending commitments after the
OL,9,Fgovernment stole its revenue-raising
OL,10,Fplan
OL,12,FLabour has vowed to crack down on tax
OL,13,Fdodgers in a bid to finance its
OL,14,Fcommitments to the NHS and schools if
OL,15,Fthe party wins the General Election,
OL,16,Fthe shadow chancellor has said.
