OL,3,CLabour vows to crack down on tax
OL,4,Cdodgers to fund NHS and schools pledges
OL,6,FThe party will look to raise #2.6
OL,7,Fbillion over the next Parliament by
OL,8,Fclosing "loopholes" in the
OL,9,Fgovernment's plans to abolish
OL,10,Fexemptions for "non-doms" - people who
OL,11,Fare not "domiciled" in the UK for tax
OL,12,Fpurposes.
OL,14,FIt also plans to raise #5 billion a
OL,15,Fyear by the end of the next Parliament
OL,16,Fby narrowing the "tax gap", which is
OL,17,Fthe difference between the amount of
OL,18,Fmoney HMRC is owed and the amount it
OL,19,Factually receives.
