OL,3,CLabour vows to crack down on tax
OL,4,Cdodgers to fund NHS and schools pledges
OL,6,FThe announcement comes a month after
OL,7,Fthe party's spending plans were thrown
OL,8,Finto disarray by the chancellor's
OL,9,Fdecision to adopt two of its revenue-
OL,10,Fraising policies at the Budget .
OL,12,FThe two policies ` abolishing "non-
OL,13,Fdom" tax exemptions and extending the
OL,14,Fwindfall tax on oil and gas companies
OL,15,F` had been earmarked by Labour to fund
OL,16,Fadditional NHS appointments and free
OL,17,Fbreakfast clubs for all primary school
OL,18,Fpupils.
