OL,3,CLabour vows to crack down on tax
OL,4,Cdodgers to fund NHS and schools pledges
OL,6,FAs a result, the party has had to find
OL,7,Fanother way to pay for those promises
OL,8,Fand now plans to raise the money it
OL,9,Fneeds by cracking down on tax avoiders.
OL,11,FShadow Chancellor Rachel Reeves said:
OL,12,F"I have been clear that everything in
OL,13,Four manifesto will be fully costed and
OL,14,Ffully funded. There will be no
OL,15,Fexceptions.
OL,17,F"That is why last month I promised to
OL,18,Fgo through all the government
OL,19,Fdocuments in an orderly way to
OL,20,Fidentify the funding streams to honour
OL,21,Four commitments to the NHS and schools.
