OL,3,CLabour vows to crack down on tax
OL,4,Cdodgers to fund NHS and schools pledges
OL,6,FIt will also consider requiring more
OL,7,Ftax schemes to be registered with HMRC
OL,8,Fto make sure they were legitimate, and
OL,9,Fplans a focus on offshore tax
OL,10,Fcompliance.
OL,12,FMs Reeves said: "At a time when
OL,13,Fworking people in Britain are being
OL,14,Fasked to pay more in tax because of
OL,15,Fthe Conservatives' economic failures,
OL,16,Fit is wrong that a minority continue
OL,17,Fto avoid paying what they owe.
