OL,3,CLabour vows to crack down on tax
OL,4,Cdodgers to fund NHS and schools pledges
OL,6,F"After 14 years in power, the
OL,7,FConservatives have failed to tackle
OL,8,Fthis issue and the tax gap remains
OL,9,Funacceptably high. With Labour, things
OL,10,Fwill change. We will take on the tax
OL,11,Fdodgers because if you make your home
OL,12,Fand do your business in Britain, then
OL,13,Fyou should pay your taxes here too.
OL,15,F"The plan we are announcing today will
OL,16,Fgive HMRC the resource it needs to go
OL,17,Fafter those who are avoiding or
OL,18,Fevading tax, and to modernise the tax
OL,19,Foffice so we have a system that is fit
OL,20,Ffor purpose."
