OL,3,CLabour vows to crack down on tax
OL,4,Cdodgers to fund NHS and schools pledges
OL,6,FWhile the measures are expected to
OL,7,Fraise more than #5 billion a year by
OL,8,Fthe end of the Parliament, only #2
OL,9,Fbillion of that money will go to
OL,10,Ffunding NHS appointments and primary
OL,11,Fschool breakfast clubs, with the rest
OL,12,Fof the money being kept back for other
OL,13,Fpriorities.
OL,15,FLabour's plans to invest more in HMRC
OL,16,Fwere welcomed by the FDA trade union,
OL,17,Fwhich said the party "recognises the
OL,18,Fscale of investment required".
