OL,6,FFDA assistant general secretary Lauren
OL,7,FCrowley said: "Only a world-class,
OL,8,Fwell-resourced tax administration can
OL,9,Fovercome new technological challenges,
OL,10,Fstay ahead of criminals and fund the
OL,11,Fnation."
OL,13,FAt last year's Budget, the government
OL,14,Fproposed measures to reduce tax
OL,15,Favoidance, including doubling the
OL,16,Fmaximum prison sentence for tax fraud,
OL,17,Fbut estimated it would have little
OL,18,Fimpact on revenues.
